Invocation Name: relax my dog
des:
Listening to this music will help your dog feel more relaxed and calm, less anxious, sleep more and be generally happier.

Playing this music is a great way to ensure that your best furry friend is feeling relaxed. If you are feeling a bit stressed out yourself, you will enjoy this soothing sounds yourself. It's very relaxing all around.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
